{"tid":2177013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有班傻仔以為係TG set  NO ONE SEE就冇人知你邊位","createTime":"2020-08-27T12:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T12:32:33.000Z","uid":315864,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94d6375f2cdf2fe8cd6fa74a2888d6b0cb4dda79","tid":2177013,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"我想分享下如果我係警察會點捉暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">假設上年8月寫個Bot入曬返有香港電話號碼做聯絡人</span></span><br />\n+852 abcd abcd個名就叫+852 abcd abcd<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HR4kAWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHR4kAWQ.png&h=a9087845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後呢班傻仔一用電話號碼reg個新acc<br />\n<span class=\"red\">就算你set no one see 都冇用</span><br />\n我部手機就出現傻仔+852 abcd abcd joined telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後揾啲channel admin <br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">只要個傻仔admin係8月後開嘅acc 我就可以望住你個tg名就知你個no.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n只要你用過電訊供應商比你嘅服務<br />\n簡單⼀個3角測量定位 你經過3,5,7個基站<br />\n再交叉對比CCTV  得咗<br />\n之後再sd啲msg啲傻仔 一㩒link就自動勾線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲咩事 唔好話你要去安全屋 你去公海我都知啊<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">不過如果班傻仔有外賣細力幫手</span><br />\n叫印尼工人姐姐幫你係印尼用太空卡開個acc<br />\n再用手機login <br />\n然後揾隻信得過嘅港豬用電腦login (有咩事都可以用電腦收tg 驗證碼俾手機login 同埋del chat)<br />\n就算我加埋印尼電話號碼我都揾你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">又或者班傻仔好醒目</span><br />\n寫個bot1號 代收msg 再auto forward去bot2號<br />\n最後bot2號再auto forward俾暴徒<br />\n咁我真係想捉你都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 今日著黑衫好熱"},{"pid":"2a8deabecb4a6a140607214e78b6f4e4c071bdd5","tid":2177013,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"4d491d6fd2e4d057797f353408cbdac9f2b0fa21","tid":2177013,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"9dcb227ad114f39b9506def8c99c48dd6fe5ac6b","tid":2177013,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"eb4c3516ae671f44b7dccea7c4f68ff66ca59173","tid":2177013,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"ff721e588010e638424300d7de9b3e37ee726f7a","tid":2177013,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e9d27da403187e7d0ad796f25bc2ea6167142a","tid":2177013,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:11:02.000Z","msg":"照拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0cc1b06f6886d43d9a7cee93392e2aa7c2a2e0","tid":2177013,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be4093769151ac23a5d8b637a034c8b7996d3425","tid":2177013,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b2514d8f43b58ea2e87fde4ef93d6fb468265a1","tid":2177013,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/l